# JivniCare Mobile — Cursor Rules

## Documentation

- Read `docs/13-AI-Development-Rules.md` before writing code.
- UI components: `docs/09-Component-Library.md`
- Design tokens (colors, typography, spacing): `docs/08-Design-System.md`
- All brand asset and brand-specific color rules are strictly in `@docs/08.1-Brand-Assets.md`. Do not read any documentation files outside of the `@docs/` folder.

## Code Conventions

- TypeScript + React Native (Expo) + NativeWind
- Use Lucide icons per `docs/08-Design-System.md` — not emoji for structural UI elements
- Match API field names exactly as documented in `docs/11-API-Contract.md`
